07:26.187 --> 07:27.612
- Yeah. You're doing a lot better than that. Come on.
<i>- (Laughs)</i>

07:27.771 --> 07:29.939
<i>We're doing pretty good.
We're doing pretty good.</i>

07:30.024 --> 07:32.942
We're looking forward to
an exciting season out there

07:33.035 --> 07:35.195
on the 1715 Fleet shipwrecks.

07:35.279 --> 07:38.698
We've got, uh,
about 18 different vessels

07:38.782 --> 07:40.959
