The captain is still
at the wheel.

11:45.788 --> 11:47.530
Yeah, you think of the big, uh,
stern going down.

11:47.614 --> 11:49.115
- Exactly, exactly.
- Yeah.

11:49.208 --> 11:51.459
And again, when these wrecks
hit the reefs

11:51.544 --> 11:53.878
they just scattered
over huge, vast areas of, uh,

11:53.963 --> 11:55.630
of ocean bottom.

11:55.715 --> 11:57.707
And this is, uh, just south
of where we're going today

11:57.791 --> 11:59.384
with Greg Bounds.

11:59.468 --> 12:01.720
NARRATOR:
Over the past year,

12:01.804 --> 12:03.972
John's colleague,
Captain Greg Bounds,

12:04.056 --> 12:06.466
has conducted
an extensive search

12:06.550 --> 12:10.353
for the scattered remains of
the 1715 Spanish Treasure Fleet.

