which deploys
electromagnetic pulses,

12:16.402 --> 12:19.070
a number of large ferrous--
Or iron-- objects

12:19.155 --> 12:22.157
have been identified
for further investigation.

12:22.316 --> 12:25.067
GREG:
I towed this magnetometer

12:25.161 --> 12:27.829
over 1,000 linear miles
back and forth

12:27.913 --> 12:31.073
on a two-square-mile area
in front of this wreck site,

12:31.167 --> 12:33.001
just to get
the highest resolution

12:33.085 --> 12:35.661
of how the ship is dispersed
across the sea floor.

12:35.755 --> 12:38.080
So, what this mag survey's done,

12:38.174 --> 12:40.917
it's given me
a true treasure map.

12:41.001 --> 12:43.261
The wreck came in here,

