first hit and lost some material
out in this water...

12:45.931 --> 12:49.342
NARRATOR: Based on Greg's
initial magnetometer survey,

12:49.435 --> 12:52.187
the team will be diving
on a possible debris field

12:52.346 --> 12:54.847
