39:03.674 --> 39:04.924
But there's no telling
what else he'll find

39:05.009 --> 39:06.584
along that trail.

39:06.668 --> 39:09.012
He's-he's found
beautiful escudo gold coins.

39:09.096 --> 39:10.254
- I think Mike even brought a...
- Yeah.

39:10.348 --> 39:11.348
We've got a couple more.

39:11.432 --> 39:12.849
Top-pocket find.

