39:45.633 --> 39:48.551
numismatically off of
the, uh, 1715 Fleet shipwrecks.

39:48.636 --> 39:50.220
- Beautiful.
- Yeah.

39:50.304 --> 39:52.389
<i>Mike's got another piece here
