39:52.473 --> 39:55.058
<i>So, this is probably my favorite
artifact that we found.</i>

39:55.217 --> 39:58.353
And, uh, this is
a solid silver lion.

39:59.555 --> 40:01.564
Wow.

40:01.723 --> 40:04.809
- That is cool.
- Truly, truly remarkable.

40:04.902 --> 40:07.487
He's sitting on his haunches,
but you can see

40:07.571 --> 40:10.573
the mane of the lion
flowing down his back,

40:10.658 --> 40:13.993
and, uh, he's got
a-a shield of some sort.

40:14.078 --> 40:16.162
Beautiful. Well done.

40:16.247 --> 40:18.748
One thing we all know is
the treasure's been out there

40:18.833 --> 40:19.999
for over 300 years.

40:20.159 --> 40:21.659
<i>It's not going anywhere</i>

40:21.743 --> 40:24.254
<i>until Mike or one of our crew
