You've got us all juiced up

40:47.945 --> 40:49.362
because there's nothing
like seeing...

40:49.521 --> 40:51.865
I mean, Gary's-Gary's dying
to get back out there now.

40:51.949 --> 40:53.941
Nothing like seeing
real treasure.

40:54.034 --> 40:56.035
All right, guys.
